{"name":"Contacts (II)","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"background","data":{"description":"<p>The character has a well-established network of reliable contacts. They can be from a variety of worlds, species and walks of life. Each contact has a specific area of knowledge and field of expertise within which he can gain access to information or further connections. The network can include old acquaintances or people the character manipulates or bribes. Which contacts are available at any given time can be resolved in various ways - either during the game at a player&rsquo;s request or the Arbiter&rsquo;s discretion, by prior agreement between player and Arbiter or based on the character&rsquo;s history.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>(II):&nbsp;</strong><strong>The character has several connections in different </strong><strong>fields, with a moderate amount of information available.</strong></p>","cost":4},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"hp1y1C9ztjsae4MT"}
