{"name":"Halfblood","permission":{"default":0,"RrWQxiSTW954To8L":3},"type":"background","data":{"description":"<p>Many humans are the offspring of mixed parentage. Halfbloods are the children of human and another Cosmic species, and although the traits of their human ancestry are typically predominant, the mark of their other blood is always evident somehow. Halfbloods often combine the tenacity of humanity with the exceptional characteristics of their other ancestry, making them potent individuals. Halfbloods may acquire attributes.</p>","cost":1},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"qGtDpN0oXVoyrCWo"}
